* 1× AN/ASQ-184 defensive management system
* 1× [[Lockheed Martin Sniper XR]] targeting pod (optional)<ref name=AFmag_Big_Squeeze>Tirpak, John A. [http://www.airforce-magazine.com/MagazineArchive/Pages/2007/October%202007/1007squeeze.aspx "The Big Squeeze."] ''Air Force Magazine'', Journal of the Air Force Association, Volume 90, Issue 10, October 2007. ISSN: 0730-6784.</ref><ref name=sniper>Kessler, Capt. Carrie L. [http://www.acc.af.mil/news/story_print.asp?id=123088382 "B-1 crews conduct TWF test; receive pod spin-up."] ''Air Force Print News Today'' , 29 February 2008. Retrieved: 30 June 2010.</ref>
